{"tid":2066203,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"羅馬尼亞取消與華合建核電廠","createTime":"2020-06-16T06:38:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-16T07:22:36.000Z","uid":25558,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"26e3e2ce58a845bf897c6d7070fae7476221742d","tid":2066203,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T06:38:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200616/2AN6OIGW22F4GNXWUS45N7UPLQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200616%2F2AN6OIGW22F4GNXWUS45N7UPLQ%2F&d=St%2FdMm9ieZWtYGJEeV6aaxzw8eMAegQd4vHbNIzLZr4%3D&h=de37c102\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200616%2F2AN6OIGW22F4GNXWUS45N7UPLQ%2F&h=b7d98fd9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200616/2AN6OIGW22F4GNXWUS45N7UPLQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n羅馬尼亞取消與華合建核電廠<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/6S7ZHDBLSVAQM3B3GJK3M2ZY7A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F6S7ZHDBLSVAQM3B3GJK3M2ZY7A.jpg&h=e7aebb77&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n羅馬尼亞將撤銷與中廣核的協議；圖為切爾納沃德核電廠。<br />\n<br />\n中國「一帶一路」倡議在東歐遭受重大挫敗。羅馬尼亞政府上周五宣佈，要求國有核電公司終止與中國廣核集團（CGN，簡稱中廣核）簽署建設兩座核反應爐的合約，政府將為該項目尋找新的合作夥伴。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n將在北約尋求合作<br />\n<br />\n據羅馬尼亞去年5月簽署的協議文件，。。。。。。。。。。。。。，稱尊重合作夥伴，要求核電公司在北約內部重新尋求合作。<br />\n<br />\n羅馬尼亞早在2014年前，開。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n，大力宣傳其在羅馬尼亞推進「一帶一路」的成果。<br />\n<br />\n不過羅馬尼亞作為北約、歐盟成員國，。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n羅馬尼亞政府去年8月拒絕與華為5G合作。<br />\n<br />\n美國之音"},{"pid":"d5150dee135223ad82c994259622321d066df92e","tid":2066203,"uid":20867,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T07:13:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cruxinvestor.com/opinions/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/Power-Plant-e1440171091880.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcruxinvestor.com%2Fopinions%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F02%2FPower-Plant-e1440171091880.jpg&h=5ec203c5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"db3e93541d043713a4345d861635f833eff8e8a5","tid":2066203,"uid":89517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T07:22:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}